data.description: Move in ready 2 bedroom 1 bath home. Living room is open to kitchen. Nice size bath and utility room.  Wood floors in bedroom and under living room carpet. Roof was replaced 2011, water heater and furnace a/c was updated in 2015. This home has a fenced yard, nice size 2 car garage and covered patio.
